Gg_sewer_simple_veroneone
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
version 1.1 for CS:S
by Dubesinhower
release date: 12/20/08
map type: gungame

features
~~~~~~~~
no weapon spawns
up to 32 spawns
easy layout
really fun, quick matches

copyright 2008 dubesinhower
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
if you want to edit or make corrections to any part of this map,
please contact me first at dubesinhower@gmail.com

change log
~~~~~~~~~~

version 1.1
~~~~~~~~~~~
added props all around level
made some lights flicker
added spark to power box
added decals of grafitti, signs, and vents
added volumetric light to manhole
awesome hobo land



this is my gg_sewer_simple map with an update. i added many things to make the environment more ghetto. it plays like the original, with added props and decals to spice up gameplay.

as always, let me know what you think!
